## Layout Specifications

### Container Dimensions
```css
.presale-widget {
  width: 450px;
  min-height: 550px;
  max-width: 100%;
  background: var(--radom-bg-primary);
  padding: 30px;
  border-radius: 25px;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  position: relative;
  overflow: hidden;
}
```

### Spacing System
```css
/* Standard Spacing */
--radom-spacing-xs: 5px;
--radom-spacing-sm: 10px;
--radom-spacing-md: 15px;
--radom-spacing-lg: 20px;
--radom-spacing-xl: 30px;

/* Component Spacing */
.widget-header {
  margin-bottom: var(--radom-spacing-xl);
}

.input-group {
  gap: var(--radom-spacing-md);
  margin-bottom: var(--radom-spacing-md);
}

.currency-grid {
  gap: var(--radom-spacing-sm);
}
```

## Component Styling

### Input Fields
```css
.radom-input {
  border: 1px solid var(--radom-border);
  border-radius: 15px;
  padding: 15px;
  background: transparent;
  color: var(--radom-text-primary);
  font-size: 16px;
}

.radom-input:focus {
  outline: none;
  border-color: var(--radom-accent-primary);
}

.radom-input::placeholder {
  color: var(--radom-text-secondary);
}
```

### Buttons
```css
.radom-button {
  border-radius: 15px;
  padding: 5px 10px;
  font-size: 14px;
  font-weight: 600;
  border: none;
  cursor: pointer;
  transition: all 0.2s ease;
}

.radom-button-primary {
  background: var(--radom-accent-primary);
  color: var(--radom-accent-text);
}

.radom-button-secondary {
  background: var(--radom-bg-secondary);
  color: var(--radom-text-primary);
}

.radom-button:disabled {
  opacity: 0.5;
  cursor: not-allowed;
}
```

### Currency Selector
```css
.currency-option {
  border: 1px solid var(--radom-border);
  border-radius: 15px;
  padding: 15px;
  background: var(--radom-bg-secondary);
  color: var(--radom-text-secondary);
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  cursor: pointer;
  transition: all 0.2s ease;
}

.currency-option:hover {
  background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
}

.currency-option.selected {
  border-color: var(--radom-accent-primary);
  background: rgba(255, 199, 0, 0.1);
}
```

### Countdown Timer
```css
.countdown-container {
  border: 1px solid var(--radom-border);
  border-radius: 10px;
  overflow: hidden;
}

.countdown-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
  width: 100%;
  padding: 15px;
}

.countdown-item {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 5px;
}

.countdown-footer {
  color: var(--radom-text-muted);
  font-size: 12px;
  text-align: center;
  background-color: var(--radom-bg-secondary);
  width: 100%;
  padding: 3px;
}
```

