  .presale-widget {
    width: 100%;
    min-height: 100vh;
    border-radius: 0;
    padding: 20px;
  }
  
  .widget-title {
    font-size: 36px;
  }
  
  .currency-grid {
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
  }
}
```

### Tablet Adaptations
```css
